00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:25.360
where we all work on the same data set in various different ways, and then we share on social media

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:29.840
what we worked on. It's a very low-stakes way to participate in the data community, to make

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:35.279
friends, to get feedback, and even to build a portfolio and just learn new things by using

00:00:35.279 --> 00:00:41.919
diverse types of data. There are hundreds of data sets that have a lot of context about them,

00:00:41.919 --> 00:00:48.480
